《财经》杂志官方微信。
An official letter from Caijing magazine.
《财经》杂志由中国证券市场研究中心主办，1998年创刊，秉承“独立、独家、独到”的新闻理念，以权威性、公正性、专业性报道见长，是政经学界决策者、研究者、管理者的必读刊物。
"Caijing" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was founded in 1998, upholding the news concept of "independence, exclusivity and originality," and providing authoritative, impartial and professional reports.
。
.
图/法新文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进 图|视觉中心总监 黎立编辑|谢丽容1. 今日概况：2月9日0—24时，31个省（自治区、直辖市）和新疆生产建设兵团报告，新增确诊病例3062例（湖北2618例），新增重症病例296例（湖北258例），新增死亡病例97例（湖北91例，安徽2例，黑龙江、江西、海南、甘肃各1例），新增疑似病例4008例（湖北2272例）。
At 0 - 24 a.m. on February 9, 31 provinces (autonomous regions, municipalities directly under the Central Government) and the Xinjiang Production and Construction Corps reported 3,062 newly confirmed cases (2,618 in Hubei), 296 new cases (258 in Hubei, 2 in Anhui, and 1 each in Heilongjiang, Jiangxi, Hainan and Gansu).
图12.新增病例：武汉大幅反复，其他地区继续趋缓图2非湖北地区继续下降。
Figure 12. New cases: Wuhan repeated significantly, other areas continue to slow down Figure 2 non-Hubei region continued to decline.
其柱状图与17年前SARS图形极为相似。
The bar chart closely resembles the SARS graphic of 17 years ago.
图3湖北非武汉地区也继续下降。
Fig. 3 Hubei non-Wuhan area also continues to decline.
图4武汉数据又有大幅波折。
Fig. 4 Wuhan data have a large fluctuation.
昨天推测武汉“洪峰主体很可能已于2月7号通过”，过于乐观。
Yesterday speculation that Wuhan "the main body of the flood peak is likely to have passed February 7," too optimistic.
看来“堰塞湖”仍需继续化解。
Seemingly "Yan Sehu" still needs to continue to dissolve.
我们没有武汉更详细数据，但从湖北发布的疑似病例数据可以做一些印证。
We do not have Wuhan more detailed data, but from Hubei released suspicious case data can do some confirmation.
湖北现有疑似病例18438人，比前一天下降5200人；集中隔离14388人，增加1460人，隔离率从55%提高到78%；当日排除疑似7194人，比前一天1128人增加6066人。
There were 18,438 suspected cases in Hubei province, 5,200 fewer than the previous day, 14,388 people were quarantined, an increase of 1,460, and the isolation rate increased from 55 to 78 percent.
排除人数大幅增加，这表明了检测能力提升，加快疑似排除自然会带来新增确诊病例更快增加。
The significant increase in the number of exclusions indicates an increase in detection capacity, and the acceleration of suspected exclusions naturally leads to a faster increase in newly diagnosed cases.
3.确诊病例增长率：武汉反弹，其他地区继续下行图5武汉增长率反弹到10%以上。
3. Confirmed case growth rate: Wuhan rebound, other regions continue to downward figure 5 Wuhan growth rate rebounded to more than 10%.
湖北非武汉地区下降到7%以下，进一步延长了倍增时间。
The non-Wuhan area of Hubei Province fell below 7%, further prolonging the doubling time.
非湖北地区继续下降。
Non-Hubei continued to decline.
在此，我们多聊几句增长率。
Here, let's talk about a few more growth rates.
有网友问：如果维持每天增加1个病例，第二天增长率是100%，第一百天增长率是1%，每天同样是1个增长，但增长率却在下降，这种下降有意义吗？我们的答复是：意义很大。
If we keep adding 1 case a day, the next day the growth rate will be 100%, the 100th day will be 1%, but the growth rate is declining.
如果维持第二天的增长率，33天就可以让地球所有人传染；如果维持第一百天的增长率，72天才会翻一番；如果每天1个恒定不变，不能排除它是传染病，但应该不是可以快速形成人群传染的“疫情“，或者是“疫情”，但得到有效控制。
If the next day's growth rate is maintained, 33 days will spread to everyone on Earth; if the 100-day growth rate is maintained, 72 days will double; if a constant daily rate is maintained, it cannot be ruled out as an infectious disease, but it should not be an "epidemic" or an "epidemic" that can spread rapidly from one population to another, but it is effectively contained.
增长率或者增长率的变化不同，体现了性质的截然不同。
Variations in growth rates, or rates of growth, reflect very different characteristics.
4.待排查疑似病例：湖北大幅下降图6待排查疑似病例第一次出现大幅下降。
4. Suspected cases to be cleared: Hubei dropped sharply Figure 6. Suspected cases first dropped sharply.
除了湖北加大排查力度，非湖北地区也有所下降。
In addition to Hubei increased clearance efforts, non-Hubei region has also declined.
这都是积极信号。
These are positive signals.
5.密切接触者追踪力度和存量图7可见非湖北地区追踪力度加大。
5. Figure 7 of the tracking intensity and inventory of close contacts shows increased tracking efforts in non-Hubei areas.
湖北该指标下降可能与集中排查现有疑似导致新增确诊跳升有关。
The decline in Hubei may be related to the centralized screening of existing suspected causes of new diagnoses of jump.
图8非湖北地区接受医学观察人数显著下降。
Fig. 8 There was a significant decrease in medical observation in non-Hubei areas.
6.在院治疗人数今天开始关注这一重要存量。
6. The number of people in hospital has begun to focus on this important stock today.
图9非湖北区已现见顶迹象，湖北地区还在增加。
Fig. 9 Non-Hubei area has seen the peak signs, Hubei area is still increasing.
7.新增治愈人数昨天将此数据纳入视野。
7. The number of new patients brought this data into view yesterday.
图10每天新治愈人数在增加。
Figure 10 The number of new cures per day is increasing.
图11非湖北地区新增治愈人数与新增确诊人数正日益接近。
Fig. 11 The number of newly diagnosed patients in non-Hubei area is approaching.
图12病死率继续小幅回升。
Figure 12 continues to show a small recovery.
小结：武汉大幅反弹，“堰塞湖”化解还需要一点时间。
Summary: Wuhan rebound substantially, "Yan Sehu" to defuse the need for a little time.
全国非湖北地区好转明显，湖北非武汉地区也在继续好转。
The improvement is obvious in non-Hubei areas of China and the non-Wuhan areas of Hubei Province continue to improve.
等待武汉数据明朗，暂缓对“顶”的推测。
Waiting for Wuhan data to be clear, suspended on the "top" speculation.
